org.deeplearning4j.nn

Class BaseNeuralNetwork

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.nn.BaseNeuralNetwork
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, Model, NeuralNetwork, Persistable, IterationListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AutoEncoder, DenoisingAutoEncoder, RBM

    public abstract class BaseNeuralNetwork
extends java.lang.Object
implements NeuralNetwork, Persistable
    Baseline class for any Neural Network used as a layer in a deep network such as an DBN
